body.name: Pellet Stove Fresh Air Intake Kit, 2" x 60" Outside Air Kit for Pellet Stove Pipe, Aluminum Flex Pipe for Corn Pellet Stove with Wall Plate Screen & Screw Hose Clamps
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Saturday, February 17. Order within 3 hrs 20 mins
features: Fitment: Air intake kit for pellet stove pipe tube inner diameter: 2"; The flex pipe stretch length: up to 60". Enough length to cover most venting/intake needs. Please confirm pellet stove size to ensure it's right before purchasing.

Durable Pellet Stove Fresh Air Intake Kit: Thickened flex hose is made of Aluminum to solve the problem of brittle flex tube and allow for being bent and extended. Heavy-duty mounting panels are made of 304 stainless steel featuring rustproof, corrosion-resistant and heat-resistant.

Save Fuel and No More Smoke Outs: 2” Outside air kit for pellet stoves provide enough fresh air to improve airflow when room air venting wasn't sufficient. And improve the efficiency of woods pellets burning to save fuel and decrease harmful gases.

Flexible Installation: The location of vent and intake be chosen as your needs. And flexibly install together with equipment you owned. Two pipe screw clamps assist firmly connection, and exterior wall plate screen with the rain hood protect your pellet stove with normal running. The pellet stove air vent kit comes with a instruction to help you easy install.
Complete Pellet Stove Exhaust Pipe Kit: 1 x Aluminum flex pipe; 2 x Pipe clamps; 1 x square exterior plate; 1 x wall plate screen; 1 x moisture barrier plate; 1 x Instruction; some screws.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good OAK for Whitfield Pellet Stove
reviews.reviewText: I have 2 of these installed with Whitfield Advantage II-T pellet stoves and they do what they're supposed to do, provide outside air to the stove. Only thing you may want to consider is if its very cold where you live, you'll see condensation on your tubing inside the house. You'll want to wrap the tube with good insulation to ensure that doesn't happen. Outside plate and weather shield are good quality and look great.
